<div class="introduction text-white">
    <h1>The art of the kitchen</h1>
    <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary my-3">Discover our kitchens</button><br>
    {{fa-icon "chevron-down" size="lg"}}
</div>
<section class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-10 py-5 text-center text-lg">
            <p>At Kitchens International we know that your kitchen is more than a room for cooking. It’s a place to be with the ones you love. A space to socialise, to entertain, to relax – the heart of your home.</p>
            <p class="mb-0"><strong>Discover the art of the kitchen.</strong></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<div class="card mb-5">
    {{image-carousel id="carousel" images=images class="carousel-home"}}
    <div class="card-block d-flex justify-content-center">
        <div class="col col-sm-8 text-center py-3">
            <h3 class="card-title">A sense of style</h3>
            <hr>
            <p class="card-text">It starts with a single idea. Or a single image.
                And it builds, layer upon layer until you’ve imagined your perfect kitchen.
                Here are just a few of the kitchen designs we’ve created. Go on, be inspired.</p>
            <button class="btn btn-outline-primary">Discover our kitchens</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="background-taupe mb-5">
    <section class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                {{#slide-in-wrapper position="left"}}
                <div class="p-4">
                    <h3>Craft &amp; proficiency</h3>
                    <hr>
                    <p>We are passionate about design.
                        And we’re equally passionate about detail,
                        every kitchen is processed through our unique project management system E.S.T &copy;,
                        ensuring everything fits. With your space, with your life.</p>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-primary">Our team &amp; service</button>
                </div>
                {{/slide-in-wrapper}}
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                {{#slide-in-wrapper position="right"}}
                <img class="img-fluid" src="/assets/images/ki-home-0004.jpg" alt="">
                {{/slide-in-wrapper}}
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center image-overlay" style="background-image: url('/assets/images/ki-home-0005.jpg')">
                    <div class="col-10 text-white text-center py-4">
                        <h3>Building relations</h3>
                        <hr class="hr-white hidden-sm-down">
                        <p>Learn about what we have done for our clients,<br>
                            their homes and their lives.</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Projects</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
<div class="background-taupe">
