                        It is said that "self-praise is no recommendation", so we have let
                        others do the talking for us!</p>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-primary">Endorsements</button>
                </div>
                {{/slide-in-wrapper}}
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                {{#slide-in-wrapper position="right"}}
                <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="/assets/images/ki-home-0010.jpg" alt="">
